<a name="section-1.1"></a>
<p></p>
<h2>1.1 Treatment of Seasonal or Perennial Allergic Rhinitis</h2>
<p class="First">RHINOCORT AQUA Nasal Spray is indicated for the treatment of nasal symptoms of seasonal or perennial allergic rhinitis in adults and children six years of age and older.</p>
